text: haey mea r yoam kaunosrei robsa ai m r n( a l laoh kaban leuk yk mk thveu cheauteahar samreab banda anak del mean chomnue der) del neang ban theroksaa pheap brisotth robsa neang haey yeung ban(brae aoy chi pri l) phlom vinhnhean robsa yeung chaul tow knong sbaun robsa neang . haey neang ban chue nouv peakyapech teanglay nei mcheasa robsa neang ning banda kompir robsa trong . haey neang kuchea anak del ban sthet knongchamnaom anak del brate b tde tam a l laoh
